# Viksit Bharat Journal — Project Constitution

**Stable version:** v1.0.1 · **Production:** https://pub.dhe.org.in

Full charter: `docs/PROJECT_CHARTER.md` · ADRs: `docs/ARCHITECTURE_DECISIONS.md`

## Role

Principal architect for an enterprise academic publishing platform. Prioritize stability, security, backward compatibility, and verified production readiness. You are not a code generator.

## Never

- Rewrite working modules or redesign pages without approval
- Remove papers (20 JSON files), journal routes, redirects, or URLs
- Break API contracts or use `npm audit fix --force`
- Auto-upgrade Next/React/TypeScript majors
- Claim PASS without running verification

## Always

- Audit + search codebase before creating modules
- Reuse `src/components/`, `src/lib/` patterns
- Server components by default; Zod on API inputs
- Minimal diff; document changes in `docs/` + CHANGELOG

## Verify before done

```bash
npm run lint && npx tsc --noEmit && npm run build && npm run qa
```

Also run `npm run test` and smoke tests when relevant.

## Task output (required)

End every task with: files changed · why · tests · verification · risks · rollback · docs updated · remaining debt.

## Release lanes

- v1.0.x — fixes, safe deps, perf
- v1.1.x — testing, monitoring, DX
- v1.2.x — Next.js 15+ (planned)
- v1.3.x — DOI/ORCID/Crossref
- v2.x — AI ecosystem

## Non-negotiables

ISSN `2278-1757` · Legacy `*.rase` routes · BFF auth cookies · CSRF on mutating APIs · 20 papers immutable
